org.zaproxy.zap.utils

Class EmptyResettableAutoCloseableIterator<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.zaproxy.zap.utils.EmptyResettableAutoCloseableIterator<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - the type of elements returned by this iterator
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCloseable, Iterator<E>, ResettableAutoCloseableIterator<E>, ResettableIterator<E>

    public final class EmptyResettableAutoCloseableIterator<E>
extends Object
implements ResettableAutoCloseableIterator<E>
    An immutable ResettableAutoCloseableIterator without behaviour.

    Useful as placeholder when a non-null ResettableAutoCloseableIterator is required but does not to have to do anything.

    Since:
    2.4.0
    See Also:
    emptyIterator(), ResettableAutoCloseableIterator
